Warning signals are:

a) signals given by turn signals or by hand;

b) sound signals;

c) switching the headlights;

d) switching on the low beam headlights in daylight;

e) activation of the alarm system, braking signals, reversing lamp, identification mark of the road train;

e) activation of the flashing orange beacon.

